es itself and keeps on going! It never ends until you lose and sink your Boat! \n \nONLINE LEADERBOARD - At the start of the game it'll ask you to allow the game through your firewall to connect to the internet so that you can submit your score to compete against other players across the globe! Who will have the top score?! \n \nMENU OPTIONS - The game is equipped with multiple options to allow you to control the overall quality of the game. You can even lower the audio and sfx. \n \nCONTROL MAPPING - Don't want to use the A \u0026 D Keys to turn left and right? Go into the Options Menu and remap it to whatever suits your fancy! \n \n \n \nHOW TO PLAY: \n \nLoad up the game, name your boat via the Profile option, click New Game, choose your difficulty level, click start, then start the level when you're ready and away you and your boat will go! \n \n \n \nCONTROLS: \n \nA = Turn Left (remappable in options menu) \n \nD = Turn Right (remappable in options menu) \n \n* A \u0026 D Turn Left and Right while going straight but once you hit a corner simply hit these again to enable a 90% turn otherwise you'll crash into an Iceberg if not you don't turn quick enough on time!","storyline":"You are the Captain of the Titanic traversing the high seas up north when suddenly all your passengers are thrown overboard. You must now compete while dodging icebergs standing in your way to save the drowning passengers left swimming in the frozen waters.","popularity":1.0,"games":[41064,17001,59516,27924,7329,26145,68287,25300,3277,8347],"tags":[21,268435489,536871198,536871251,536871553,536872010,536872152,536872868,536873064,536873300,536873403,536873838,536874705,536876274,536885116,536888057,1073741826],"developers":[15508],"publishers":[15508],"game_engines":[439],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[2],"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[286,339,641,1098,1240,1956,2152,2388,2491,2926,3793,5362,14204,17145],"themes":[21],"genres":[33],"first_release_date":1526342400000,"platforms":[6],"re